longBusinessSummary: Grand Ocean Advanced Resources Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in coal mining business in Inner Mongolia, the People's Republic of China. It produces and sells coal; and provides management services. The company was formerly known as DeTeam Company Limited and changed its name to Grand Ocean Advanced Resources Company Limited in June 2015. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.
